      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for bind fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-1519: high CPU load during insecure delegation validation due to excessive NSEC3 iterations (bsc#1260805).\n",
